# AlbFatherQW
$din_zajava_albfather = {
	act 'Write a statement':
		cls
		minut += 1
		AlbFather = 2
		gs 'stat'
		'"So you agree to write a statement, huh"?,the Captain nodded quietely. "You're a smart girl and chose the right side. Come with me in the car then and everything will be arranged quickly."'

		act 'Go with Chernov':
			cls
			minut += 1
			AlbZaDay = daystart
			gs 'stat'
			'You wrote and signed the statement asked by the captain, and he let you go.'

			act 'Escape.':gt 'gorodok'
		end
	end
}

$din_zajava_albfather_no2 = {
	act 'Refuse':
		cls
		minut += 1
		AlbFather = -1
		gs 'stat'
		'You resolutely refused to write a statement for the captain. The captain sighed sadly,shaking his head  "I see. You have just made powerful enemies girl." Without another word he turned and left'

		act 'Warn Albina':
			cls
			minut += 1 
			AlbFrend = 1
			ZvezdEnd = 1
			gs 'stat'
			'You quickly dialed Albina's number and told her what had happened. Albina remained silent for a few seconds than with a thoughtful 'thank you', she simply hang up.'

			act 'Escape':gt 'gorodok'
		end
	end
}

$din_zajava_albfather_no = {
	act 'Not sure if you should write the statement':
		cls
		minut += 1 
		gs 'stat'
		'Seeing your doubts and uncertainty, the captain began to try persuading you to write the statement. "Think about the consequences. Albina will not help you get out of this mess. If not you,then somebody else will speak sooner or later.In the end we will get her and you both. Cooperate with us now and we can take it easy on you.But do it now while we lack more concrete evidence or we have no deal girl!"'

		if intel >= 80:
			act 'Ask him why you should tell him anything':
				cls
				minut += 1
				gs 'stat'
				'You asked the captain if they were all so good, then why did they need you. The captain replied after a moment, "Frankly, this whole case isn't within our jurisdiction, and to act without direct evidence against such a dangerous person,could have dire consequences if it ends bad. A statement would guarantee the success of this operation."'
				dynamic $din_zajava_albfather
				dynamic $din_zajava_albfather_no2
			end
		end

		dynamic $din_zajava_albfather
		dynamic $din_zajava_albfather_no2
	end
}

gs 'stat'
'Suddenly a black car pulls to a stop right next to you. A man in a nice suit and shades waves at you to come closer. Pulling out a badge from his suit, he opens it for you to see and read. "Captain Chernov. State Security Service, he says in a serious deep voice" With suprise evident in your face you check the documents' authenticity. Finally, with suprise still in your voice you ask softly, "Why are you here? This has to be a mistake. I haven't done anything.." With the confident tone of a trained Captain, Chernov replied grimly "No mistake, you are <<$name>> <<$surname>>, let''s step aside and talk."'
act 'Go with Chernov':
	cls
	minut += 1
	gs 'stat'
	' You walked away with Captain Chernov. Along the way, you noticed that sticking under his armpit was a holster with a gun. In a serious tone Chernov begins speaking "<<$name>>. I know that you are new to the team of Zvezdushki. I know this team is about much more than just dancing. The Zvezdushki will fall soon, with or without your help. It''s not even so important if you help, what is important is that when the case gets in motion, the whole town will know what you did in this team. Even if you didn't have an important role in it, serious or not, that will not stop the gossip.You will be given a big fine, We will inform your parents, your school, and it will be put on your record with the police. But all this can be avoided. "'

	act 'Ask him how you can avoid it':
		cls
		minut += 1
		gs 'stat'

		if age < 18:'Worriedly you asked captain Chernov if it was possible to avoid publicity and the consequences that would follow. Captain Chernov turned to you and said "We could work something out. If you write to the security service claiming that Albina Barlovskaya enticed you into prostitution. After all you are an underage. This will mean extra trouble for Albina."'
		if age >= 18:' Worriedly you asked captain Chernov if it was possible to avoid publicity and the consequences that would follow. Captain Chernov turned to you and said "We could work something out. If you write to the security service claiming that Albina Barlovskaya enticed you into prostitution."'

		'Captain Chernov paused, giving you time to think it over before he continued. "If you write an application, you will be charged as the victim, not an accomplice and your name will not be given to publicity. Actually, you don't even have to write an application. Make a statement and Iâ€™ll take care of the rest. Next time we meet I can have the papers with me."' 

		if intel >= 70:
			act 'Ask him why the security service is investigating this instead of the police':
				cls
				minut += 1
				gs 'stat'
				'You asked what was so important with Albina, that  had the security service searching this case instead of the police. Captain grinned and replied "I underestimated you, you''re a smart girl. Okay, I''ll play my cards straight with you instead.  Do you know who the father of Albina is? Barlovsky Boris, a retired police colonel. He served as chief of police in this very town.He is supposed to be retired now, but still has a great many connections with the police. "'

				if intel >= 75:
					act 'Tell him that he still hasn't answered your question':
						cls
						minut += 1
						gs 'stat'
						'You told the captain that he still had not answered the question, why now sudden interest in the affairs of Albina from the security service. The captain nodded, "It''s very simple. Albina''s father decided to go into politics and is running for mayor of this town. There are certain 'elements' that want to stop him. What  better way than arresting his daughter as a criminal engaged in a prostitution."'
						dynamic $din_zajava_albfather
						dynamic $din_zajava_albfather_no
					end
				end

				dynamic $din_zajava_albfather
				dynamic $din_zajava_albfather_no
			end
		end

		dynamic $din_zajava_albfather
		dynamic $din_zajava_albfather_no
	end
end

